**Story**
once upon a time, in a  forest, there lived a monkey who resided on a jamoon(berry)
tree, which was on the banks of a river. In the same forest,
there lived a crocodile and his wife. One day the crocodile came to the banksof 
the river and rested under the tree. The kind hearted monkey offeref him some fruits.
 The crocodile came back the next day for more fruit and soon the monkey and crocodile
 became friends.

 One day the monkey sent some fruits to the crocodile's wife. she liked the fruits , but
  was not happy that her husband is spending time with the monkey. 